title: Dead 2 Me
lyrics:
Low-down way you're feeling, 
The sexy things you do
Baby, baby, baby, 
Let me talk to you
I just love to whisper 
In your sexy ear

Tell you that I love you, 

Take away your fear

Destroy your inhibitions, 

Ridin' back the day

Low-down, slow down, 

Keeping low down 

In that funky way



Higher, higher, higher, 

How high can you go

Ride me high this morning, 

Ride me high some more



The way you move your body, 

It is a crying shame

I won't tell nobody 

If you will do the same

If you leave tomorrow, 

One thing that's for sure

The more you get, 

The more you've got, 

The more you want some more



Higher, higher, higher, 

How high can you go

Ride me high this morning, 

Ride me high some more

Higher, higher, higher, 

How high can you go

Ride me high this morning, 

Ride me high some more
